<P>
RADIATION SICKNESS KILLS 1, HURTS 3 IN ESTONIA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A tiny sliver of highly radioactive metal poisoned the atmosphere in the 
kitchen of a village home, killing a man and a dog and making three others 
severely ill. 
</P>
<P>
 There was no clear explanation how the sliver found its way into the home. 
</P>
<P>
 It was discovered after members of the family became sick. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
