<DOCID> 100402 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
November 20, 1994, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Food; Part H; Page 16; Column 1 
