AWARD UPHELD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 * God Bless America! This must be the only nation where a confessed kidnaper 
can get off after serving only one year in prison, and then collect close to a 
million dollars in damages for a broken ankle suffered when the police caught 
him in the act of picking up the ransom money ("Verdict in Brutality Case 
Upheld," Nov. 8). 
</P>
<P>
 With the blessing of the U.S. Supreme Court, yet! And to think that so many 
