OUT WITH DORNAN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Well, it didn't take very long for Orange County's favorite loudmouth, "B1" 
Bob Dornan, to show his true hypocritical stripes once again. 
</P>
<P>
 It took less than three days for "B1" Bob, one of the "term limits heroes," to 
break his promise to his constituents. 
</P>
<P>
 After his ninth term, "B1" Bob was supposed to gracefully retire from 
Congress. 
</P>
<P>
 Now he says if his bid for the presidency in 1996 fails (and all sane people 
hope it will fail miserably) he might go for a 10th term. 
</P>
<P>
 I think this time "B1" Bob should lead by example and step down and leave us 
in peace. 
</P>
<P>
