 L.A. City College 72, Moorpark 71 -- Saipele Tuialii hit a 10-foot baseline 
jumper with three seconds left to give the visiting Cubs (5-0) a nonconference 
victory over the Raiders (2-1). WOMEN'S BASKETBALL 
</P>
