but the Mustangs shot only 27%. MEN'S SOCCER 
</P>
<P>
 The Master's 6, Bartlesville (Okla.) Wesleyan 4 -- Paul Smith scored the 
tie-breaking goal in the 77th minute, leading the Mustangs (16-5-3) to third 
place in the National Christian College Athletic Assn. tournament in Cleveland, 
