<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA112094-0365 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 100661 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
November 20, 1994, Sunday, Ventura West Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 1; Column 3 
